name: The Samurai
description:
Lone Island is a series of virtual worlds that life could be if you are to be alone on an island.

#3 The Samurai

An unworthy blade meets death
For honor left a long time ago
I surpassed every trial
Yet none to tell what I've done

Orange skies glaring
Like my sword soaring
Seeking someone who could match
Just give me some scratch.
